KALI GUIDE

Static Network Setup:
  Config File:
   /etc/network/interfaces
------------------------------------------------------------------------
   
  Format:
  
  auto <name of interface ex. eth0, ens18>
  iface <name of interface> inet <dhcp or static>
          address <IP address --- ex. 172.2.t.100>
          netmask <subnet mask --- ex. 255.255.0.0>
------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Applying changes:
  sudo systemctl restart networking
